metadata.name: Early Retirement
metadata.description:
Luke had always dreamed of retiring early and moving to the mountains. For years he worked tirelessly as a software developer, always taking on more challenging projects. He quickly gained a reputation and opportunities for new projects continued to flow in...but ... Luke had found NFTs...

As a result of smart trading, Luke was able to amass a small fortune in savings and illiquid JPG investments. It was time to retire and head to the mountains. Luke spent his days exploring the trails, fishing in the lake, and soaking in the natural beauty of his surroundings. But his laptop was always nearby in case a surprise mint hit his radar.
